acker News 的热门话题，涵盖移动隐私系统商业化、AI 代理交互标准 WebMCP、AI 编码追溯工具及科技政策争议等前沿动态。","summary":"文章精选了 Hacker News 过去 24 小时内的十大热点。核心内容包括：Motorola 与 GrapheneOS 达成合作，推动隐私强化系统进入主流硬件；/e/OS 与 Jolla 手机展示了欧洲去谷歌化生态的最新进展；技术层面，WebMCP 协议的发布预示着网站将为 AI 代理进行标准化重构，而 git-memento 工具则尝试解决 AI 编码的可追溯性问题。此外，文章还报道了 Anthropic 产品在 macOS 上的性能缺陷、微软社区管理的公关危机，以及美国 NIST 限制外籍研究人员引发的科研竞争力担忧。","archive_path":"data/articles/2026/03/RAW_209f78fd.json","topicTag":"ai-llm","category":"Business_Tech","sourceName":"SuperTechFans","resourceType":"ARTICLE","readTime":74,"score":87},{"id":"RAW_93516857","title":"上门安装 OpenClaw，年入百万？","link":"https://www.ifanr.com/1656340?utm_source=rss&utm_medium=rss&utm_campaign=","date":"2026-03-02 16:27:35","archive_path":"data/articles/2026/03/RAW_93516857.json","topicTag":"ai-llm","category":"Business_Tech","sourceName":"爱范儿","resourceType":"ARTICLE","readTime":11,"score":84},{"id":"RAW_6c7a60ca","title":"2026-03-02 Hacker News Top Stories #","link":"https://supertechfans.com/cn/post/2026-03-02-HackerNews/","date":"2026-03-02 09:40:09","archive_path":"data/articles/2026/03/RAW_6c7a60ca.json","topicTag":"ai-llm","category":"Business_Tech","sourceName":"SuperTechFans","resourceType":"ARTICLE","readTime":72,"score":87},{"id":"RAW_33b5613e","title":"腾讯研究院司晓：AI 要让人放心，把人放大","link":"https://mp.weixin.qq.com/s?__biz=MjM5OTE0ODA2MQ==&mid=2650996034&idx=1&sn=120b501a97fad41f61e41e1f91f6fbfe","date":"2026-03-02 08:30:00","archive_path":"data/articles/2026/03/RAW_33b5613e.json","topicTag":"ai-llm","category":"Business_Tech","sourceName":"腾讯研究院","resourceType":"ARTICLE","readTime":9,"score":83},{"id":"RAW_2c3c4f56","title":"微软 CEO 纳德拉：Office 早已转型！模型架构距离关键创新或只差一步!只要有真实落地，AI 就谈不上说是泡沫！看好量子计算与 AI 融合","link":"https://mp.weixin.qq.com/s?__biz=MjM5ODI5Njc2MA==&mid=2655936685&idx=1&sn=f528274ac46cde8ffb546f81670c9429","date":"2026-03-02 04:58:00","archive_path":"data/articles/2026/03/RAW_2c3c4f56.json","topicTag":"ai-llm","category":"Business_Tech","sourceName":"51CTO技术栈","resourceType":"ARTICLE","readTim